{
  "texts": [
    "It can be used in binary as well as multi-class classification problem.",
    "For example in project evaluation where the outcome of success is divided into number of success indicators (Wohlin et al. 2000).",
    "Kappa score is more useful than accuracy when dealing with imbalanced data.",
    "Some common measures to evaluate the business performance and interests are summarized as follows:",
    "Return on Equity (ROE): ROE is a financial measure calculated by dividing a company's net income by its total equity."
  ]
}